<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Looting, how it should work</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?TheBlack[BCK]">TheBlack[BCK]</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 2:30 p.m. 23/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Looting, how it should work<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1648" TARGET=_self>Loot: an absurdity</A> (Klan)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>

<BR>Players should only be lootable when their death comes from PvP combat, and then only lootable by the player or group that did 50% or more of the total damage to that player. In any other cases the corpse should not be lootable. Be that as it may I don't see any signs that Verant is making changes to the game at this stage, let alone making any improvoements for the PvP server.
<P>I do agree with the poster's prognosis, it will be hard on everyone the higher in level players rise, assuming of course that higher levels can be killed in PvP conflicts at all.
<P>&gt; Well the PvP system has no chance to be a success as long as the
<BR>&gt; loot systme is active.
<BR>&gt; Why ?
<P>&gt; 2 reasons:
<BR>&gt; - PvP was only tested by low levels characters : so none has
<BR>&gt; really experienced a heavy loss. But how could you imagine the
<BR>&gt; warrior seeing its breast plate looted, or the mage his flourish
<BR>&gt; robe wich took him weeks to obtain ?
<BR>&gt; Be realist , until now we losse almost nothing, but in a few
<BR>&gt; week, when you'll see you first chain mail bought being looted
<BR>&gt; an hour after. Several day of saving lost in 10 seconds.
<BR>&gt; - Anyone can loot you anytime : i mean you are a 15th level
<BR>&gt; warriior, you die in east common because of a griffin (example),
<BR>&gt; a 4th level coming near see your corpse, loot your. Great for
<BR>&gt; him ! He has now in his backpack your chain mail legs, so aroung
<BR>&gt; 70 pp , not abd for a 4th level isnt it ? And the victi, zill
<BR>&gt; never knoz zho loot him. The worst i think is that if you die
<BR>&gt; from a creature, you can looted too : Verant told us
<BR>&gt; "Everquest is a game where you die". I mean this is
<BR>&gt; manly a PVE game, and we add the PvP dimension, it start to be
<BR>&gt; unplayable for us !
<P>&gt; Solution :
<BR>&gt; NO MORE LOOT POSSIBLE, ONLY MONETARY POSSESSIONS
<P>&gt; I think this is the price to pay to have a viable system. If
<BR>&gt; this doesnt change in a few weeks we'll see many disgusted
<BR>&gt; players believe me.
<P>&gt; Klan
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
